<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ow prattles of Faith; &amp; <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ath it in his mouth, I be|leeue, but all hath not <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">aith, saith the Apostle. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">aith is a rare iewell: a <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ewell I call it, for what|soeuer thou touchest by <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">aith, it becomes thine <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">wne, but so that it<NOTE PLACE="marg">Faith is a rare Iewell no larger then Ele|ction.</NOTE> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">uches nothing but the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">wne proper obiect, to <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">it, that whereunto the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">romise of GOD in his <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ord directs it: and a rare <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">well I call it, because it no larger then Electi|on, it may be common to <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">any in respect of pro|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ssion, but proper to <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">aints onely, in respect of
