<P>But here may be de|manded,<NOTE PLACE="marg">Our man|sions in re|spect of Gods de|cree were prepared before the world. <HI>Mat.</HI> 25. 34</NOTE> how saith o<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> Sauiour, <HI>I goe to prepare<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> place for you?</HI> Was it n<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> prepared before the fou<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">|dation of the world? <HI>Co<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> ye blessed of my Father, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> herit the Kingdome prep|red for you from the fo<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">
