<P>For the first: Christ Ie|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">s<NOTE PLACE="marg">And this preparati|on stands in these three.</NOTE> hath ascended vnto <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">auen to possesse it for <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> and vnto vs, to sease
