<P>Now that our Sauiour<NOTE PLACE="marg"><HI>Limbus pa|trum</HI> alto|gether e|lumbat, can finde no footing in this place.</NOTE> saith, <HI>I goe to prepare a place for you:</HI> we haue shewed <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">n what sense hee saith it. And therefore they are farre mistaken who abuse this place, to proue, that the way to the heauenly Mansions was vnpassa|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">le, and heauen inaccessi|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">le before the resurrecti|on &amp; ascention of Christ: <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">o affirme the Prolocu|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ors<NOTE PLACE="marg"><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> on Heb. 9. v. 8.</NOTE> for <HI>Babell,</HI> that the
