<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">he first Tabernacle was standing.</HI></P>
<P>For answering where|of<NOTE PLACE="marg">Another place vin|dicate fro~ the h<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">nds of Papists which they would abuse to proue that none of the godly before Christ, went into heauen.</NOTE> we must know, that the Apostles purpose there, is <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">o declare vnto the <HI>He|brewes,</HI> that the seruice of the Leuiticall Priest-hood &amp; first Tabernacle, could not of it selfe, giue salua|tion, but figured that sal|uation which comes by the bloud of the high Priest. Now albeit the Leuiticall seruice of it <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> could neyther saue Priest nor people, yet so many of them as were spirituall, and in vsing of the Typicall sacrifice,
